definition: the temporal property of two things happening at the same time
details:
noun
- the temporal property of two things happening at the same time
= example: the temporal property of two things happening at the same time
= synonyms: concurrence
- the quality of occupying the same position or area in space
= example: the quality of occupying the same position or area in space
- an event that might have been arranged although it was really accidental
